bindsym --release $mod+t exec picom-trans -s 100

https://i3wm.org/docs/userguide.html#keybindings

Some tools (such as import or xdotool) might be unable to run upon a KeyPress event, because the keyboard/pointer is still grabbed. 
For these situations, the --release flag can be used, which will execute the command after the keys have been released."
